Build Instructions
==================

Bundle Monitor is an Eclipse plug-in developed in PDE. To open the projects:

1) Check out the source code using Git:

    git clone git://github.com/njbartlett/bundlemonitor.git

2) In Eclipse select File > Import > Existing Projects into Workspace and click Next.

3) Click Browse, and navigate to the `bundlemonitor` directory created by Git.

4) Ensure all sub-projects are checked and click Finish. Do NOT check the box labelled "Copy projects into workspace".